title: BRIEF-FORTEC Elektronik FY result up at EUR 1.87 mln
text:
BRIEF-FORTEC Elektronik FY result up at EUR 1.87 mln Sept 23 
Sept 23 FORTEC Elektronik AG : 
* Turnover in FY 2014/15 was 45.9 million euros ($51.02 million) compared to 45.4 million euros last year 
* FY EBT was 2.5 million euros (previus year: 2.2 million euros) 
* Year's result of 1.87 million euros clearly topped that of last year of 1.54 million euros, thus confirming forecast given for BY 2014/15 
* Board of Directors again suggests an unchanged dividend payment of 50 cent per share Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8996 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
